    "tag": "exercise",
    "title": "Exercise 10.1: Project Setup",
    "desc": "30 minutes",
    "body": [
      {
        "card": "Task:",
        "items": [
          "Create Git repo: <code>student-grade-manager</code>",
          "Use Claude Code to scaffold Maven project",
          "Add dependencies: Gson, JUnit 5, Mockito",
          "Create initial classes: <code>Student</code>, <code>Grade</code>, <code>GradeManager</code>",
          "First commit on <code>main</code>: &ldquo;Initial project structure&rdquo;",
          "Create branch: <code>feature/core-logic</code>",
          "<strong>Verify:</strong> <code>mvn compile</code> works"
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "content",
    "mod": "10",
    "tag": "exercise",
    "title": "Exercise 10.2: Implementation + Tests",
    "desc": "60 minutes",
    "body": [
      {
        "card": "On feature branch:",
        "items": [
          "Implement <code>Student</code> (name, ID, list of grades)",
          "Implement <code>GradeManager</code> (add student, add grade, calculate average, save/load JSON)",
          "Write JUnit tests &mdash; use Claude Code + write some by hand",
          "Use TDD for at least one method",
          "Regular commits with meaningful messages",
          "<strong>Verify:</strong> <code>mvn test</code> all green"
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "content",
    "mod": "10",
    "tag": "exercise",
    "title": "Exercise 10.3: Quality + Pipeline",
    "desc": "45 minutes",
    "body": [
      {
        "card": "Task:",
        "items": [
          "Merge feature branch to main",
          "Run <code>mvn checkstyle:check pmd:check spotbugs:check</code>",
          "Fix all violations (AI help OK, but understand each fix)",
          "Add JaCoCo &mdash; target 70%+ coverage",
          "Write Jenkinsfile with stages: Build, Test, Quality, Package",
          "Final commit: &ldquo;Add CI pipeline and quality gates&rdquo;",
          "<strong>Verify:</strong> <code>mvn clean package</code> succeeds with zero warnings"
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
